### Tracker row with run history
GET http://localhost:4101/pipeline/Pipelines?$filter=name eq 'Shipments'&$expand=runs($orderby=startTime desc;$top=5)

### Status convenience function
GET http://localhost:4101/pipeline/status(name='Shipments')

### All run history, most recent first
GET http://localhost:4101/pipeline/PipelineRuns?$orderby=startTime desc&$top=20

### Flush — clears the local table and resets lastSync / lastKey on the
### tracker so the next run starts from scratch.
POST http://localhost:4101/pipeline/flush
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"Shipments"}
